#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:5
msgid "System"
msgstr "系统"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:7
msgid ""
"The *System* tab allows you to set resolution, scripting console preferences, sound, graphics cards, and "
"internationalization."
msgstr "在 *系统* 标签页，用户可以设置分辨率，脚本控制台设置，声卡显卡设置，以及语言设置。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:10
msgid ""
"If your hardware does not support some of the options described on this page, then they will either not show up or "
"get corrected on startup. If this happens do not worry, you can either consult your computer manual to find a "
"supported value or just let Blender correct it."
msgstr ""
"如果用户的硬件不支持本页面描述的一些选项，这些选项要么会隐藏或者在启动时更正。如果这种情况发生了，不要担心，可以查询"
"电脑的使用手册，找到支持的参数，或者让Blender自动更正。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:17
msgid "User Preferences System tab."
msgstr "用户设置的系统标签页。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:21
msgid "General"
msgstr "常规项"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:30
msgid "Frame Server Port"
msgstr "帧服务器端口"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:26
msgid ""
"TCP/IP port used in conjunction with the IP Address of the machine for frameserver rendering. Used when working "
"with distributed rendering. Avoid changing this port value unless it is conflicting with already existing service "
"ports used by your Operating System and/or other software. Always consult your operating system documentation and "
"services or consult your system administrator before changing this value."
msgstr ""
"TCP/IP端口，与机器的IP地址结合用于帧服务器渲染。在使用分布渲染时使用。尽量不要更改端口值，除非该值与现有的系统服务或"
"其他软件使用的端口存在冲突。修改该数值前，请查看操作系统文档或咨询售后，又或者咨询系统管理员。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:35
msgid "Console Scrollback"
msgstr "控制台回查行数"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:33
msgid ""
"The number of lines, buffered in memory of the console window. Useful for debugging purposes and command-line "
"rendering."
msgstr "控制台窗口缓存的最大信息行数。这可使你向上追溯系统运行状态，来排除故障和命令行渲染。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:40
msgid "Sound"
msgstr "声音"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:53
msgid "Audio Device"
msgstr "音频设备"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:43
msgid "Sets the audio engine to use to process and output audio."
msgstr "设置处理和输出音频的音频引擎。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:45 ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:101
#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:119
msgid "None"
msgstr "无"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:46
msgid "No Audio support (audio strips can still be loaded normally)."
msgstr "禁用声音(但可以正常加载音频片段)。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:48
msgid "SDL"
msgstr "SDL"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:48
msgid ""
"Uses Simple Direct Media Layer API from `libsdl.org <https://www.libsdl.org>`__ to render sounds directly to the "
"sound device output. Very useful for sequencer strips editing."
msgstr ""
"使用来自 `libsdl.org <https://www.libsdl.org>`__ 的Simple Direct Media Layer API，将音频直接渲染到音频输出设备，适用"
"于序列片段编辑。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:53
msgid "OpenAL"
msgstr "OpenAL"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:51
msgid ""
"Provides buffered sound rendering with 3D/spatial support. Used for 3D source support by *Speaker Objects* and the "
"*Game Engine*."
msgstr "为缓存音频渲染提供3D音效支持，用于受 *扬声器物体* 和 *游戏引擎* 支持的3D声源。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:56
msgid "Sound Options"
msgstr "声音选项"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:58
msgid ""
"These settings control how sound behaves during live playback within Blender and are only available with *SDL* or "
"*OpenAL*. To control these settings for exporting sound see the :ref:`Encoding Panel <render-output-video-encoding-"
"panel>` and :ref:`Audio Panel <data-scenes-audio>`."
msgstr ""
"这些设置用于控制Blender中实时播放时的声音表现，只胡 *SDL* 或 *OpenAL* 可供选择。关于输出音频的控制设置请参考 :ref:`"
"编码面板 <render-output-video-encoding-panel>` and :ref:`Audio Panel <data-scenes-audio>`。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:65
msgid "Channels"
msgstr "通道"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:65
msgid ""
"Sets the audio channel count. Available options are: *Mono*, *Stereo*, *4 Channels*, *5.1 Surround*, *7.1 Surround*."
msgstr "设置音频通道总数，可用选项有： *立体声* ， *4声道* ， *5.1声道环绕* ， *7.1声道环绕*。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:68
msgid "Mixing Buffer"
msgstr "混合缓冲区"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:68
msgid ""
"Sets the number of samples used by the audio mixing buffer. Available options are: *512*, *1024*, *2048*, *4096*, "
"*8192*, *16384*, and *32768*."
msgstr "设置混音缓冲区采样数。可用选项有: *512* , *1024* , *2048*, *4096* , *8192*, *16384*, 和 *32768*。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:71
msgid "Sample Rate"
msgstr "采样率"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:71
msgid ""
"Sets the audio `sampling rate <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sampling_(signal_processing)#Sampling_rate>`__. "
"Available options are: *44.1 Khz*, *48 Khz*, *96 Khz* and *192 Khz*."
msgstr ""
"设置音频 `采样率 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sampling_(signal_processing)#Sampling_rate>`__。可用选项有： *44.1 "
"Khz*, *48 Khz*, *96 Khz* 和 *192 Khz*。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:77
msgid "Sample Format"
msgstr "采样格式"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:74
msgid ""
"Sets the audio sample format. Available options are: *32 bit float*, *8 bit Unsigned*, *16 Bits Signed*, *24 Bits "
"Signed*, *32 Bits Signed*, *32 Bits Float*, and *64 Bits Float*."
msgstr ""
"设置音频的采样格式，可用选项有： *32位浮点*, *8位无符号整型*, *16位带符号整型*, *24位带符号整型*, *32位带符号整型*, "
"*32位浮点*, 和 *64位浮点*。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:82
msgid "Screencast"
msgstr "程序截屏"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:84
msgid "These settings are used to control the frame rate for recording a :ref:`Screencast <info-screencast>`."
msgstr "这些设置用于控制 :ref:`屏幕 <info-screencast>` 录制的帧率。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:86
msgid "FPS"
msgstr "帧率"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:87
msgid "The frame rate for screencast playback."
msgstr "屏幕录制的回放帧率。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:90
msgid "Wait Timer"
msgstr "计时器"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:89
msgid "Time in milliseconds between each frame recorded for screencast."
msgstr "相邻两帧截频的间隔时间，单位毫秒。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:93
msgid "Compute Device"
msgstr "计算设备"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:95
msgid ""
"The *Compute Device* option allows the user to change the computing device the :doc:`Cycles </render/cycles/index>` "
"render engine uses to render images. Cycles can use either the CPU or certain GPU's to render images, for more "
"information see the :doc:`GPU Rendering </render/cycles/gpu_rendering>` page."
msgstr ""
"*计算设备* 用于修改 :doc:`Cycles </render/cycles/index>` 用于渲染图片的计算设备。Cycles可以使用CPU或者特定的GPU渲染"
"图片，更多相关信息见 the :doc:`GPU渲染 </render/cycles/gpu_rendering>` 页面。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:101
msgid ""
"When set to *None* or when the only option is *None*: the CPU will be used as the computing device for the Cycles "
"Renderer."
msgstr "当选择 *无* 或者只能选择 *无* 时，将使用CPU作为Cycles的计算设备。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:104
msgid "CUDA"
msgstr "CUDA"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:104
msgid ""
"If the system has a compatible Nvidia CUDA enabled graphics card you will be able to use it to render with the :doc:"
"`Cycles </render/cycles/features>` render engine."
msgstr "如果显卡兼容Nvidia CUDA ，可以使用显卡进行 :doc:`Cycles </render/cycles/features>` 渲染。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:108
msgid "OpenCL"
msgstr "OpenCL"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:107
msgid "If the system has a compatible AMD OpenCL device, it will show up an option for rendering with Cycles."
msgstr "如果显卡兼容 AMD OpenCL，会显示该选项。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:113
msgid "OpenSubdiv Compute"
msgstr "OpenSubdiv计算"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:115
msgid ""
"The options here will set the compute device used by OpenSubdiv for the :doc:`Subdivision Surface Modifier </"
"modeling/modifiers/generate/subsurf>`."
msgstr "该选项用于设置 :doc:`细分曲面修改器 </modeling/modifiers/generate/subsurf>` OpenSubdiv使用的计算设备。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:119
msgid ""
"Disables any OpenSubdiv compute devices, makes sure legacy subdivision method is used. Use this option when "
"OpenSubdiv causes any bugs or regressions."
msgstr "禁用OpenSubdiv计算设备，确保使用老式(legacy)细分方法。当OpenSubdiv导致错误或回归时，使用此选项。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:123
msgid "CPU"
msgstr "CPU"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:122
msgid ""
"Single threaded CPU implementation. It is mainly useful in cases when GPU compute is possible and threaded CPU "
"option causes artifacts (it is unlikely to happen, but still possible)."
msgstr "单线程CPU实现。当GPU计算可行，但多线程CPU选项存在瑕疵(不太可能发生，但还是有可能的)时使用。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:125
msgid "OpenMP"
msgstr "OpenMP"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:126
msgid "Multi-threaded CPU implementation. Use it for maximum performance in cases when GPU compute is not available."
msgstr "多线程CPU实现。当GPU计算不可用时，使用该选项最大化利用机器性能。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:127
msgid "GLSL Transform Feedback"
msgstr "GLSL变换反馈"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:128
msgid "Uses GPU to perform calculations, has minimal requirements to video card and driver."
msgstr "使用GPU进行计算，对视频卡和驱动有最低要求。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:132
msgid "GLSL Compute"
msgstr "GLSL计算"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:130
msgid ""
"Uses GPU to perform calculations, supposed to be more efficient than *Transform Feedback* but also has higher "
"requirements to video card and driver."
msgstr "使用GPU来进行计算，应该比 *变换反馈* 更有效，但对显卡和驱动程序也有更高的配置要求。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:135
msgid "OpenGL"
msgstr "OpenGL"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:138
msgid "Clip Alpha"
msgstr "限制 Alpha"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:138
msgid ""
"Clip alpha below this threshold in the 3D View. Note that the default is set to a low value to prevent issues on "
"some GPU's."
msgstr "在3D视图中限制低于此值的alpha。注意，为防止出现问题，默认值很低。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:140
msgid "Mipmaps"
msgstr "多级纹理"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:141
msgid ""
"Scale textures for 3D View using :term:`mip-map` filtering. This increases display quality, but uses more memory."
msgstr "使用 :term:`Mip映射` 过滤来规划贴图，这会提高精度，但会占用更多的内存。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:142
msgid "GPU Mipmap Generation"
msgstr "GPU 多级纹理生成"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:143
msgid "Generate mip-maps on the GPU instead of the CPU."
msgstr "使用GPU生成多级纹理，而非CPU。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:144
msgid "16 Bit Float Textures"
msgstr "16 位浮点纹理图"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:145
msgid "Enables the use of 16 Bit per component Texture Images (floating point images)."
msgstr "给每单位图像纹理使用16位纹理图像(浮点图像)。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:155
msgid "Selection"
msgstr "选中项"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:147
msgid "Selection method to use for selecting."
msgstr "用于选择的选择方法。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:149 ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:176
msgid "Automatic"
msgstr "自动"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:150
msgid "Automatically chooses the best setting depending on your OS, GPU, and drivers."
msgstr "基于操作系统、CPU和驱动，自动选择最佳设置。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:151
msgid "OpenGL Select"
msgstr "OpenGL选择"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:152
msgid "Legacy OpenGL selection method for legacy hardware."
msgstr "老式硬件使用的OpenGL选择方法。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:155
msgid "OpenGL Occlusion Queries"
msgstr "OpenGL遮面查询"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:154
msgid ""
"More optimized OpenGL selection method. Use this method if you are using an `OpenSubdiv Compute`_ compute device."
msgstr "优化的OpenGL选择方法。如果使用 `OpenSubdiv计算`_ 设备，使用这种方法。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:160
msgid "OpenGL Depth Picking"
msgstr "OpenGL Depth Picking"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:158
msgid ""
"This option uses an alternative method of picking which uses depth information to select the front-most elements. "
"It is only used for selecting with the cursor (not border select, lasso, circle select, etc.)."
msgstr "该选项使用另一种深度信息拾取方法，来选择最靠前的元素。仅适用于鼠标点选(不能框选、套索，圈选等)。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:161
msgid "Performance varies depending on your OpenGL hardware and drivers."
msgstr "具体性能视OpenGL硬件和驱动有所不同。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:166
msgid "Anisotropic Filtering"
msgstr "各向异性过滤"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:163
msgid ""
"Sets the level of anisotropic filtering. This improves the quality of how textures are drawn at the cost of "
"performance. Available Options are: *Off* (No Filtering), *2x*, *4x*, *8x*, and *16x*."
msgstr ""
"设置各向异性过滤级别，提高以性能为代价时的贴图绘制品质。可用选项有： *关闭* (无过滤), *2x*, *4x*, *8x*, 和 *16x*。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:171 ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:189
msgid "Window Draw Method"
msgstr "窗口绘制方法"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:174
msgid "Specifies the Window Draw Method used to display Blender Window(s)."
msgstr "定义Blender视窗的绘制方法。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:177
msgid "Automatically set based on graphics card and driver."
msgstr "根据驱动器和显卡自动选择。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:179
msgid "Triple Buffer"
msgstr "三重缓存"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:179
msgid ""
"Use a third buffer for minimal redraws at the cost of more memory. If you have a capable GPU, this is the best and "
"faster method of redraw."
msgstr ""
"为细致的刷新屏幕使用第三层缓存，这会消耗更多的内存，当然如果你有个吊炸天的GPU（核弹显卡什么的），你可开启这个选项，"
"blender的动态显示将会变得又快又棒。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:182
msgid "Overlap"
msgstr "重叠"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:182
msgid ""
"Redraw all overlapping regions. Minimal memory usage, but more redraws. Recommended for some graphics cards and "
"drivers combinations."
msgstr "刷新所有重叠区，在尽量减少内存消耗的前提下多次刷新，推荐给一些使用显卡和驱动器搭配的用户。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:185
msgid "Overlap Flip"
msgstr "重叠反转"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:185
msgid ""
"Redraw all overlapping regions. Minimal memory usage, but more redraws (for graphics drivers that do flipping). "
"Recommended for some graphic cards and drivers combinations."
msgstr ""
"刷新所有重叠区，在尽量减少内存消耗的前提下多次刷新（图像驱动器会自动跳过），推荐给一些使用显卡和驱动搭配的用户。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:189
msgid "Full"
msgstr "全部"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:188
msgid ""
"Do a full redraw each time. Only use for reference, or when all else fails. Useful for certain cards with bad to no "
"OpenGL acceleration at all."
msgstr "每次都完全重绘。测试和其他选项都失败的情况下使用。有些卡没有或者很烂的opengl加速的时候使用。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:199
msgid "Multi-Sampling"
msgstr "多重采样"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:194
msgid "This enables :term:`FSAA` for smoother drawing, at the expense of some performance."
msgstr "开启 :term:`FSAA` 带来更平滑的绘制, 会消耗一定的性能。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:198
msgid ""
"This is known to cause selection issues on some configurations, see: :ref:`troubleshooting-3dview-invalid-"
"selection`."
msgstr "可能会引起选择上的一些问题，参见: :ref:`troubleshooting-3dview-invalid-selection`。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:208
msgid "Region Overlap"
msgstr "区域重叠"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:202
msgid ""
"This checkbox will enable Blender to draw regions overlapping the 3D View. It means that the *Tool Shelf* and "
"*Properties regions*, will be drawn overlapping the 3D View editor."
msgstr ""
"这个选项可使Blender在3D视窗中绘制重叠区域，也就是说， *工具栏* 和 *属性区块* (T面板和N面板)，可以3D视窗上重叠显示。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:206
msgid ""
"If you have a capable graphics card and drivers with *Triple Buffer* support, clicking the checkbox will enable the "
"overlapping regions to be drawn using the *Triple Buffer* method, which will also enable them to be drawn using "
"Alpha, showing the 3D View contents through the regions."
msgstr ""
"如果用的是还不错的显卡和驱动器，支持 *三重缓存* ，勾选该选项，将启用 *三重缓存* 方法来绘制重叠区域，同时会显示透明效"
"果，透过重叠区域可以看到3D视图。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:213
msgid "Text Draw Options"
msgstr "文本绘制选项"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:211
msgid ""
"Enable interface text anti-aliasing. When disabled, texts are drawn using text straight render (filling only "
"absolute pixels)."
msgstr "激活界面的文字图形抗锯齿。禁用后，将使用直接渲染方法绘制文本(仅填充绝对像素)。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:216
msgid "Textures"
msgstr "纹理"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:222
msgid "Limit Size"
msgstr "尺寸限制"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:219
msgid ""
"Limit the maximum resolution for pictures used in textured display to save memory. The limit options are specified "
"in a square of pixels (e.g: the option 256 means a texture of 256×256 pixels). This is useful for game engineers, "
"whereas the texture limit matches paging blocks of the textures in the target graphic card memory. Available "
"Options are: *Off* (No limit), *128*, *256*, *512*, *1024*, *2048*, *4096*, and *8192*."
msgstr ""
"限制纹理中图片显示的最大分辨率，以此来节省内存。这个限制设置是以正方形的像素块来运作的(比如，256表示256x256x像素的纹"
"理)。这个选项在游戏引擎中非常管用，然而纹理限制与目标显卡内存中存储的分类数据块相吻合。可用选项有：*关闭* (无限"
"制)， *128* , *256* , *512*, *1024*, *2048*, *4096* 和 *8192*。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:225
msgid "Time Out"
msgstr "超时间隔"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:225
msgid ""
"Time since last access of a GL texture in seconds, after which it is freed. Set to 0 to keep textures allocated. "
"Minimum: *0*, Maximum: *3600*."
msgstr "GL贴图在被访问后释放的时间，数值为0表示保留纹理。最小值: *0*, 最大值: *3600*。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:229
msgid "Collection Rate"
msgstr "采集频率"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:228
msgid "Number of seconds between each run of the GL texture garbage collector. Minimum: *0*, Maximum: *3600*."
msgstr "GL纹理回收计算的间隔秒数，最小值: *0*, 最大值: *3600*。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:240
msgid "Image Draw Method"
msgstr "图像绘制方法"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:232
msgid "Method to draw images as the following options are supported:"
msgstr "支持以下图像绘制方法："

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:234
msgid "2D Texture"
msgstr "2D纹理"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:235 ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:239
msgid "Uses CPU for display transform and draws images as a 2D texture."
msgstr "使用CPU显示变换和绘制图像为2D纹理。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:236
msgid "GLSL"
msgstr "GLSL"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:237
msgid "Fastest method using GLSL for display transform and draws images as a 2D texture."
msgstr "最快的方法，使用GLSL显示变化和绘制图像为2D纹理。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:240
msgid "Draw Pixels"
msgstr "显示像素"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:243
msgid "Sequencer/Clip Editor"
msgstr "序列/剪辑编辑器"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:248
msgid "Memory Cache Limit"
msgstr "内存缓存限值"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:246
msgid ""
"Upper limit of the Sequencer's memory cache (megabytes). For optimum Clip editor and Sequencer performance, high "
"values are recommended."
msgstr "序列编辑器的内存缓存上限 (MB)。要达到剪辑编辑器和序列编辑器的最佳使用性能，推荐使用较高的数值。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:253
msgid "Solid OpenGL Lights"
msgstr "OpenGL 实色光照"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:255
msgid ""
"*Solid OpenGL Lights* are used to light the 3D View, mostly during *Solid view*. Lighting is constant and position "
"\"world\" based. There are three virtual light sources, also called OpenGL auxiliary lamps, used to illuminate 3D "
"View scenes, which will not display in renders."
msgstr ""
"*OpenGL实色光照* 是用来在3D视窗中照明的，多数用在 *实体视图*。光照是恒定的，并且位置是基于“世界”的。OpenGL中有三种实"
"色光源，也可称之为OpenGL辅助灯，用来照亮3D视窗场景，这种照明不会在渲染结果中显示。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:260
msgid ""
"The Lamp icons allow the user to enable or disable OpenGL lamps. At least one of the three auxiliary OpenGL Lamps "
"must remain enabled for the 3D View. The lamps are equal, their difference is their positioning and colors. You can "
"control the direction of the lamps, as well as their diffuse and specular colors."
msgstr ""
"你可点击灯泡图标来开启或关闭OpenGL实色光照，然而你不能把他们全禁用，至少会有一种实色光照处于开启状态。这三种灯光差不"
"多，他们的区别在于不同的位置和颜色。你可控制灯的方向和漫射高光颜色可选的选项有。"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:265
msgid "Use"
msgstr "使用"

#: ../../manual/preferences/system.rst:266
msgid "Toggles the specific lamp."
msgstr "切换指定灯光。"

